# Implementation Plan - 10 Week AI Challenge Tracker

## Goal Description
Create a responsive, premium-designed web application to track a "10 Week AI Challenge". The app will persist data to a local disk store (JSON file) and allow the user to view weekly challenges, update progress with notes, and mark weeks as complete.

## User Review Required
- **Persistence Strategy**: We will use a local `weeks.json` file in the project directory for simplicity and portability. This meets the "disk store" requirement.
- **Framework**: Next.js 14+ (App Router) with Tailwind CSS.

